.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt SLANT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm slant
.Nd client for remote system monitoring
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm slant
.Op Fl o Ar order
.Ar url...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility displays system statistics gathered from
.Ar url .
The hosts must be running
.Xr slant-collectd 1 ,
whose statistics must be available from the CGI script.
Its arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl o Ar order
Default order of host listing.
May be
.Ar cmdline
for natural order,
.Ar host
for hostname,
.Ar cpu
for immediate CPU, or
.Ar mdm
for immediate memory.
